Usage: reset_spare_insts [-help] {-cell <cellName> | -inst <instName> | -hinst <hinstName>}

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cellName>     # spare cell name (wild card) to be reset
                     # (string, optional)
-hinst <hinstName>   # spare hierarchical inst name (wild card) to be reset
                     # (string, optional)
-inst <instName>     # spare inst name (wild card) to be reset
                     # (string, optional)